                     <interp inst="t18390304-904-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18390304-904-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18390304-cd-23" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18390304-904-offence-1 t18390304-cd-23"></join>11th of feb<lb></lb>ruary</rs>, 10<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the monies of <persName id="t18390304-name-191" type="victimName">
